Package: gix
Title: Search a Git repository
Description: gix is a package to index and search a Git repository
    using the Xapian search engine. NOTE: The package is in a very
    early development phase and not functional yet.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Stefan", "Widgren", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "stefan.widgren@gmail.com"))
Imports:
    git2r,
    xapr
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2),
    methods
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/stewid/gix
Type: Package
BugReports: https://github.com/stewid/gix/issues
LazyData: true
Biarch: true
NeedsCompilation: no
Date: 2014-09-13
Collate:
    'gix.r'
    'gix-package.r'
    'gixit.r'
